{
  "enabled": true,
  "name": "create-api-route",
  "description": "Create standard FastAPI route structure for new API files",
  "when": {
    "type": "fileCreated",
    "patterns": [
      "backend/app/routers/**/*.py"
    ]
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "A new API route file has been created at ${FILE}. Please use Desktop Commander MCP to add the standard FastAPI route structure:\n\n```python\n\"\"\"\n[Route name] API endpoints\n\nThis module provides API endpoints for [feature description].\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom fastapi import APIRouter, Depends, HTTPException, status\nfrom sqlalchemy.ext.asyncio import AsyncSession\nfrom typing import List, Optional\n\nfrom ..core.database import get_db\nfrom ..core.user_context import require_user_id\nfrom ..models.db_models import [ModelName]\nfrom pydantic import BaseModel\n\n# Router configuration\nrouter = APIRouter(\n    prefix=\"/api/[route-name]\",\n    tags=\"[route-name]\"\n)\n\n# Request/Response models\nclass [Name]Request(BaseModel):\n    \"\"\"Request model for [operation]\"\"\"\n    pass\n\nclass [Name]Response(BaseModel):\n    \"\"\"Response model for [operation]\"\"\"\n    pass\n\n# Endpoints\n@router.get(\"/\")\nasync def list_items(\n    user_id: int = Depends(require_user_id),\n    db: AsyncSession = Depends(get_db)\n) -> List[[Name]Response]:\n    \"\"\"List all items\"\"\"\n    # TODO: Implement\n    return []\n\n@router.post(\"/\")\nasync def create_item(\n    request: [Name]Request,\n    user_id: int = Depends(require_user_id),\n    db: AsyncSession = Depends(get_db)\n) -> [Name]Response:\n    \"\"\"Create a new item\"\"\"\n    # TODO: Implement\n    raise HTTPException(\n        status_code=status.HTTP_501_NOT_IMPLEMENTED,\n        detail=\"Not implemented yet\"\n    )\n```\n\nUse mcp_desktop_commander_mcp_write_file() to write the template. Replace [placeholders] with appropriate names based on the filename."
  },
  "blocking": false
}